          <p class='first-para'>
            I thank the Minister again, but I am still not entirely happy with his response on who would be likely to go to prison. It could be an individual who has failed to do whatever they should have done or done something that they should not. If something is done at the direction of, say, the board, does the whole board go to prison?</p><p>
            I have raised the issue, and I would be grateful if it could be given a little more thought. Perhaps, the Minister could write to me and we could consider the matter a little further. At this stage, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
